'''Ceejin markaad wax liqayso''' waxay dhacdaa marka cuntada aan si fiican loo calalin, oo ay marin habaabto, oo ay xidho marinnada hawada. 

Ceejin waxaa lagu xalliyaa gargaarka degdegga ah (''hoos ka akhriso'') iyo, haddii ay sii socoto, iyadoo [[:en:List_of_emergency_telephone_numbers#Africa|la wacayo adeegyada caafimaadka degdegga ah]].

== Gargaarka degdega ah ==
Qaar ka mid ah farsamooyinka gacanta ayaa xallin kara ceejinta (hoos ka akhri).

Ka sokow, waxaa jira qaar ka mid ah aaladaha "ka soo hor jeedaa-ceejin" suuqa (LifeVac iyo Dechoker).

=== Gargaarka degdega ah ee dhibbanayaasha caadiga ah ===
Qaybta hore waa qufac. 

Haddii dhibbanuhu aanu qufaci karin,<ref>American Red Cross, [https://web.archive.org/web/20200210071651/https://redcross.org/content/dam/redcross/atg/PDF_s/ConsciousChokingPoster_EN.pdf Conscious Choking] </ref> ku isticmaal laba farsamooyinka gacanta (eeg labada sawir ee hoose).

Si loo helo natiijo ka sii wanaagsan, iskudar markooda: samee farsamo kasta qiyaastii 5 jeer, oo u beddel farsamada kale, oo ku celi kuwan si joogto ah.

Dadka uurka leh iyo kuwa buuran waxay u baahan yihiin inay wax ka beddelaan farsamooyinkan gacanta (hoos ka akhri).

Dhallaanka (ka yar 1 sano) waxay u baahan yihiin inay wax ka beddelaan farsamooyinkan gacanta (hoos ka akhri).  

Haddi margadu sii socoto, [[:en:List_of_emergency_telephone_numbers#Africa|wac adeega caafimaadka degdega ah]].
 
Dhibbanaha waxa laga yaabaa inuu miyir beelo muddo ka dib (hoos ka akhri), kaas oo u baahan "[[Ceejin#Kicinta wadnaha sambabada ka soo hor jeedaa-ceejin, caadiga ah|kicinta wadnaha sambabada ka soo hor jeedaa-ceejin]]".
