=== Marka dhibbanuhu miyir daboolan yahay ===
Waxaa loo baahan yahay: "[[Ceejin#Kicinta wadnaha sambabada ka soo hor jeedaa-ceejin, caadiga ah|kicinta wadnaha sambabada ka soo hor jeedaa-ceejin]]"

