==== Kicinta wadnaha sambabada ka soo hor jeedaa-ceejin, caadiga ah ====
[[File:Chest compressions.gif|thumb|Cadaadiska laabta ee kicinta wadnaha sambabada.]]
[[File:Insulfation2.jpg|thumb|Hawo-qaadid (neefsashada samatabbixinta) ee kicinta wadnaha sambabada. Dhallaanka, isticmaal afka si aad isku mar u daboosho afka iyo sanka dhallaanka.]]
Waxa loo baahan yahay in [[:en:List_of_emergency_telephone_numbers#Africa|laga waco adeega caafimaadka degdega ah]]. 

Dhig dhibbanaha oo jiifa, wejiga kor u taagaya. 

Samee "kicinta wadnaha sambabada ka soo hor jeedaa-ceejin ee dhallaanka" dhibbanaha, si joogto ah:

* 30 cadaadis oo ku yaal qeybta hoose ee bartamaha xabadka.
* Haddii shayga xayiran uu soo baxo, isku day inaad ka saarto. Alaabta waa la soo saari karaa, ama lama saari karaa,  laakiin dib u soo kicinta wadnaha sambabada waa inay sii socotaa ilaa dhibbanuhu si caadi ah u neefsado.
* Xir sanka dhibbanaha. Geli hawada adoo samaynaya hawo-qaadid (neefta samatabbixinta) afka-ka-afka. Geli hawo mar kale adiga oo samaynaya hawo kale oo isku mid ah (neef samatabbixin ah).
* U rog madaxa dhibbanaha hore iyo gadaal, si aad u beddesho xoogaa booskiisa. Soo geli hawo adiga oo samaynaya hawo-qaadid (neefta samatabbixinta) afka-ka-afka. Dib u soo geli hawo mar kale adiga oo samaynaya hawo kale oo isku mid ah (neef samatabbixin ah).

Ku celi, si joogto ah, tallaabooyinkan oo dhan, laga bilaabo kii ugu horreeyay (30-kii cadaadis).

==== Kicinta wadnaha sambabada ka soo hor jeedaa-ceejin, ee dhallaanka (ka yar 1 sano) ====
Waxa loo baahan yahay in [[:en:List_of_emergency_telephone_numbers#Africa|laga waco adeega caafimaadka degdega ah]].

Dhig dhallaanka oo jiifa, wejiga kor u taagaya. Madaxa dhallaanka waa inuu u eegaa hore, had iyo jeer. 

U samee dhallaanka "kicinta wadnaha sambabada ka soo hor jeedaa-ceejin ee dhallaanka", si joogto ah:

* Laga soo bilaabo dhinaca ilmaha: 30 cadaadis, oo lagu sameeyay laba farood oo ku yaal nuska hoose ee xabadka.
* Haddii shayga xayiran uu soo baxo, isku day inaad ka saarto. Alaabta waa la soo saari karaa, ama lama saari karaa,  laakiin dib u soo kicinta wadnaha sambabada waa inay sii socotaa ilaa dhibbanuhu si caadi ah u neefsado.
* Isticmaalka afka, ku dabool afka ilmaha iyo sanka ilmaha, isku mar. U soo geli hawo habkaas (hawo-qaadid ama neefta samatabbixinta). Dib u soo geli hawo mar kale (hawo kale oo isku mid ah ama neef samatabbixin ah).
* Waxaa lagu talinayaa in madaxa dhallaanka uu sii wato eegidda hore, oo aan u janjeerin, sababaha ah leexinta madaxa waxay ku cidhiidhi kartaa marinnada hawadu ee ilmaha.

Ku celi, si joogto ah, tallaabooyinkan oo dhan, laga bilaabo kii ugu horreeyay (30-kii cadaadis).

